revision.text:
'''2345.com''' is a [[China|Chinese]] [[web directory]] founded in 2005.<ref name=ITTimes>{{cite news|url=http://www.it-times.de/news/giant-interactive-schluckt-2345com-27081/|title=Giant Interactive schluckt 2345.com|publisher=IT Times|date=2 November 2010|accessdate=5 June 2012|language=de}}</ref> The website is the second most used web directory in China.<ref name=MW>{{cite news|url=http://businesswatch.21cbh.com/index.php?m=content&c=index&a=show&catid=9&id=203647|title=Giant Interactive and Sequoia Capital Buy 2345.com|date=29 October 2010|publisher=Morning Whistle|accessdate=5 June 2012|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130116195312/http://businesswatch.21cbh.com/index.php?m=content&c=index&a=show&catid=9&id=203647|archive-date=2013-01-16|dead-url=yes|df=}}</ref> It is ranked 47th place in China and has a worldwide ranking of 419 on [[Alexa Internet|Alexa]].<ref name=Biz>{{cite web|title=2345.com|url=http://bizinformation.com.my/www.2345.com|publisher=Biz Information|accessdate=5 June 2012|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130221151609/http://bizinformation.com.my/www.2345.com|archive-date=2013-02-21|dead-url=yes|df=}}</ref><ref name=alexa>{{cite web|title=2345.com Web Ranking|url=http://www.alexa.com/siteinfo/2345.com|publisher=Alexa|accessdate=5 June 2012}}</ref> It is hosted at Abitcool China Inc. Beijing, China.

