The '''''Anales de Tecamachalco''''' or '''Annals of Tecamachalco''' is an anonymous [[Nahuatl]]-language historical manuscript held by the Library of the [[University of Texas]].

==Publication==
*{{cite book |author =Peñafiel, Antonio |year=1903 |title=Anales de Tecamachalco |series=Colección de documentos para la historia mexicana}}
*{{cite book |author1=Solís, Eustaquio Celestino |author2=Luis Reyes García |year=1992 |title=Anales de Tecamachalco: 1398-1590 |isbn=968-16-3797-6}}

