{{Use dmy dates|date=August 2015}} {{Use British English|date=August 2015}} {{ infobox bibliographic database | title = Anthropological Index Online | image = | caption = | producer = [[Royal Anthropological Institute of Great Britain and Ireland]] | country = [[United Kingdom]] | history = | languages = | providers = [[EBSCO Information Services|EBSCO Publishing]] | cost = Free (individuals), subscription (institutions) | disciplines = Anthropology | depth = Index | formats = Journal, trade & magazine articles | temporal = 1957 to present | geospatial = | number = | updates = | p_title = Anthropological Index | p_dates = | ISSN = 0003-5467 | web = https://aio.therai.org.uk/ | titles = https://aio.therai.org.uk/aio.php?action=searchjournals }}
The '''Anthropological Index Online''' is an [[academic journal]] indexing service for [[anthropology]].
The service indexes the journals received by The Anthropology Library at [[The British Museum]] (formerly at the [[Ethnography at the British Museum#Museum of Mankind|Museum of Mankind]]), which receives periodicals in all branches of anthropology from academic institutions and publishers around the world. It is a collaboration between the [[Royal Anthropological Institute of Great Britain and Ireland]] and the Anthropology Department at the [[University of Kent]]. It is also available under licence from [[EBSCO Information Services]] as part of Anthropology Plus.
There are several hundred thousand records to date, the earliest from the late 1950s. Subject coverage is [[cultural anthropology]]/[[social anthropology]], [[physical anthropology]], [[archaeology]] and [[linguistics]]. The index is regularly updated.
== External links == * {{Official website|https://aio.therai.org.uk/}}
[[Category:Online databases]] [[Category:British Museum]] [[Category:Anthropology literature]]

