{{italic title}}
The ''Diccionario enciclopédico hispano-americano de literatura, ciencias y artes'' (1887-1899) was a [[Spanish language]] [[general encyclopedia]] produced by Montaner y Simón in [[Barcelona]], [[Spain]].<ref>{{cite book|title=Guide to the Study and Use of Reference Books |author1= [[Alice B. Kroeger|Alice Bertha Kroeger]] |author2= [[Isadore Gilbert Mudge]] |year=1917 |edition=3rd |location=Chicago |publisher=American Library Association |chapter=Encyclopedias: Spanish |chapterurl= https://books.google.com/books?id=Rr8zAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA38 }}</ref>

