An '''explanatory dictionary''' or '''monolingual dictionary''' is a [[dictionary]] that gives additional information, e. g. on [[pronunciation]], [[grammar]], meaning, [[etymology]] etc.<ref>{{cite book | title=An Introduction to Lexicography|url=http://www.ciil-ebooks.net/html/lexico/link5.htm | section=Types of Dictionaries}}</ref> Such dictionaries are usually meant for the native speakers of the language.

